snippet.title: [11Wk Danoni] EZ (daniwell - UZ)
snippet.description:
jk it's not EZ at all

This time around, it's yet another keymode with 11 keys! Though I think I'll cover the other 11k variations that I haven't made a video of yet after making the video of the chart (more like two charts, actually) that I talked about in my previous video since those keymodes aren't featured in those charts! Whoops, that was a big hint, wasn't it?

This keymode is definitely more different than the two 11k variations that I made a video of before though! the 7k part is still the same, but the 4k part is not arranged in a way that it resembles the arrow keys! The other four keys are technically two sets of 2k, the first one being the ones represented by arrows, which default keys are TY (between the left and right side of 7k), and the other set being the ones with the faces, which default keys are 1 and 0 (alternate keys for them is 2 and - respectively)! I moved the keys for the faces to E and O instead though! 

Also unlike the earlier 11k variations, this one is not considered as one of the meta, at least by the time this video was made! But I think out of all the non-meta 11k, this one has the most charts? (11ik comes close though!)

Shorts ver: https://youtu.be/bedHU9IQeC0

I hope you decide to try out danoni for yourself! ....or else

#danoni

~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~

Song: daniwell - UZ
Maker: 青白錠剤
Chart Link: https://superkuppabros.sakura.ne.jp/hp/danoni/danoni/uz.html?scoreId=3
